modShortDescription: Stock zeds do absolutely no damage to the following block tags: Earth, Dirt, Stone, Metal, Ore, fterrain, terrGravel, terrSnow.
modDescription:
Stock [zeds](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-zombies/) do absolutely no damage to the following block tags: Earth, Dirt, Stone, Metal, Ore, fterrain, terrGravel, terrSnow.

They still attack and do the animation but nothing is damaged. If there are enough of them they will pile up and eventually kill each other off.
